global minimal = "pitstopnum racenum"

global exp = "bet earnings winvalue shistakes slostakes swealth totalprpayout experiment"

global demo = "female age age2 culture_asian culture_other weekinc_1 weekinc_2 weekinc_3  wealth_1 wealth_2"
// 

global edu = "perfuni international* englishspeaker mum_school mum_qual mum_hiqual dad_school dad_qual dad_hiqual" 

global psych = "risk SBI_reminisce SBI_anticipate SBI_moment opt02 opt04 self_esteem_composite locus_of_control happy luckyans "
// excluded: bettingjust i.relig i.financesat i.gamblingjust i.political i.haslucky i.watchover

global physio = "BMI lefthand vegi alcohol_dummy smoke depression"
// excluded: medication




/* 
 labels
 */

/*
gen pse = psexpectation / 1000

gen female = 0
replace female = 1 if gender == 1

gen age2 = age*age

replace winpc = 2^-100 if winpc == 0
sum winpc
*/

replace culture = lower(culture)

gen culture_asian = 0
local asian "`"australian born chinese"' `"bangladesh"' `"beijing"' `"buddish"' `"cantonese"' `"chian"' `"china"' `"chinese"' `"hindu"' `"hong kong"' `"india"' `"indian"' `"indonesia"' `"indonesian"' `"iran"' `"korea"' `"korean"' `"malaysia"' `"malaysian"' `"myanmar"' `"nanjing"' `"pakistan"' `"philippines"' `"prc"' `"singapore"' `"singapore "' `"south korea"' `"southeast asian"' `"sri lanka"' `"srilanka"' `"taiwan"' `"vietnam"' `"vietnamese"'"
foreach a of local asian {
   replace culture_asian = 1 if culture == "`a'"
}

gen culture_other = 0
local other "`"american"' `"belgium"' `"european"' `"n/a"' `"sweden"' `"usa"' `"venezuela"'"
foreach a of local other {
di "`a'"
   replace culture_other = 1 if culture == "`a'"
}
